gomodel:SYNGO_1972  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Endogenous tPA containing dense-core granules colocalize with presynaptic marker synapsin (Fig. 1). Recombinant tPA-EYFP is co-packaged with BDNF-mCherry in presynaptic dense-core vesicles (Fig. 2).. Experimental description: Hippocampal neurons from 18-day-old embryonic rats were cultured on 18-mm diameter round glass #1 cover slips (p. ...)" ;
